00:40:22.460 --> 00:40:23.395
Magkakaroon ba ng katuturan iyon?

00:40:24.129 --> 00:40:27.432
Kung ang tanging bagay lang na
halos hindi ko maintindihan...

00:40:28.667 --> 00:40:32.237
kimchi lang naman,

00:40:33.805 --> 00:40:36.007
Maiintindihan kaya ni Min Woo?

00:40:39.110 --> 00:40:41.046
Mahal, tinatakot mo ako ngayon.

00:40:43.982 --> 00:40:45.383
Talaga...

00:40:50.588 --> 00:40:51.423
Naliligaw kami.

00:41:02.167 --> 00:41:03.735
ayaw ko ng kimchi.

00:41:09.474 --> 00:41:13.945
(Kimchi)

